snippet.title: Amber Heard With Child Confirmed: Tries Avoiding Prison Time
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Baby Announcement Might Be Another Publicity Stunt To Avoid Jail Time.

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

Amber Heard, 35, a popular actress is coming into serious media attention as Amber’s new motherhood is claimed to benefit her career. Although not all agreed, in her announcement, Heard said that having a baby is “one of the most fundamental parts of our destinies,” which led some readers to think she had bad motives behind her post. 

#AmberHeard #AmberHeardBaby
